# YAML / JSON contract linting via Stoplight Spectral

* repo: [https://github.com/stoplightio/spectral](https://github.com/stoplightio/spectral)
  rev: v6.11.0
  hooks:

  * id: spectral-lint
    name: spectral lint (yaml/json)
    entry: npx spectral lint
    language: node
    types: \[yaml, json]
